text: @FedExHelp hi there my package has been at Charles De Gaulle for 24 hours and is scheduled for tomorrow by 12. Will I receive it?

@powerpuffb1tch Hello, this is Matt. We apologize for this issue. Please DM @FedExHelp the full name on the shipment, full delivery address, tracking, email & phone numbers so I may further look into this for you.
